cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CY, cs.SI 

This paper deals with natural language processing (NLP) and specifically focuses on contextualized word embeddings such as BERT. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses machine learning techniques and optimization, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper discusses bias and fairness, which could fall under cs.CY (Computers and Society) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
